content: We did have a lot of NL name examples, didn't we? Can't find them. There is something in Example on Simplifier, but it's unreadable.
they would all have changed because of the decisions made at DevDays

Hi Marc, we have examples of HumanName in Patient, Practitioner, and RelatedPerson:
- https://simplifier.net/NL-BasicComponents/nl-core-patient-example-1/xmlview
- https://simplifier.net/NL-BasicComponents/nl-core-practitioner-example-1
- https://simplifier.net/NL-BasicComponents/nl-core-relatedperson-example-1

If you have examples that would like to add, please let us know, so we can have a more complete set of examples
https://chat.fhir.org/#narrow/stream/179166-implementers/topic/IPS.20Name.20Question - may be of interest in Netherlands given nordic discussion about vervegsoel
